<p><b>Interactive Chord Applet:</b> It's Here!</p>

<p><a href = "GIG/gig.htm">Guitar Intelli-Guitar 1.0 by Arthur Asuncion</a> is a first-class chord applet with virtually unlimited capo and tuning support.  G.I.G. includes Composer 1.0, a mini-sequencer of guitar progressions.  And best of all, it's free to use.  Visit G.I.G. today!</p>

<hr>

<p><b>Additional Notes:</b></p>

<ul>
<li>In the patterns, <i>D = down-strum</i>, <i>U = up-strum</i>, <i>M = multiple-string pluck</i>, and <i>S = string slap</i>.
<li>The guitar in the background clip uses <a href="picking1.htm">Picking Pattern 1</a> to play this chord progression:<br> <b> D - A/C# - Bm - G</b>

<li>Turn on your speakers to hear the MIDI files. If you still cannot hear any music, check the <i>SW Synth</i> levels in <i>Volume Control</i>.
</ul>

